jecución</title><link href="/graphql-guide-spanish/aprender/execution" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Ejecución" /><published>2018-07-12T00:00:00+00:00</published><updated>2018-07-12T00:00:00+00:00</updated><id>/graphql-guide-spanish/aprender/execution</id><content type="html" xml:base="/graphql-guide-spanish/aprender/execution"></content><author><name></name></author><summary type="html"></summary></entry><entry><title type="html">Introspección</title><link href="/graphql-guide-spanish/aprender/introspeccion" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Introspección" /><published>2018-07-11T00:00:00+00:00</published><updated>2018-07-11T00:00:00+00:00</updated><id>/graphql-guide-spanish/aprender/introspeccion</id><content type="html" xml:base="/graphql-guide-spanish/aprender/introspeccion"></content><author><name></name></author><summary type="html"></summary></entry><entry><title type="html">Introducción</title><link href="/graphql-guide-spanish/buenas%20pr%C3%A1cticas/introduction" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Introducción" /><published>2018-07-10T00:00:00+00:00</published><updated>2018-07-10T00:00:00+00:00</updated><id>/graphql-guide-spanish/buenas%20pr%C3%A1cticas/introduction</id><content type="html" xml:base="/graphql-guide-spanish/buenas%20pr%C3%A1cticas/introduction"></content><author><name></name></author><summary type="html"></summary></entry><entry><title type="html">Pensando en Grafos</title><link href="/graphql-guide-spanish/buenas%20pr%C3%A1cticas/thinking-in-graphs" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Pensando en Grafos" /><published>2018-07-09T00:00:00+00:00</published><updated>2018-07-09T00:00:00+00:00</updated><id>/graphql-guide-spanish/buenas%20pr%C3%A1cticas/thinking-in-graphs</id><content type="html" xml:base="/graphql-guide-spanish/buenas%20pr%C3%A1cticas/thinking-in-graphs"></content><author><name></name></author><summary type="html"></summary></entry><entry><title type="html">Sirviendo sobre HTTP</title><link href="/graphq